At least 166 people were killed in Ethiopia after an iconic musician, Haacaaluu Hundeessaa, was murdered last week.

Prime Minister Ahmed responded to the violence by sending in troops, shutting off the internet and arresting opposition leaders. https://t.co/C8BCrezP9t
